languages.text: "Мы гордимся своими палатами. Отсюда поступает энергия, что питает главный корабельный двигатель. Есть на судне и другие двигатели, но наш — самый могучий. В общем, важную работу делаем".
"We are proud of our chambers. Power feeds the ship's main engine from here. There are other drives on the ship, but ours is the mightiest. That's to say, we do important work."

languages.text: «Nos sentimos orgullosos de nuestras cámaras. Aquí se produce la energía que se suministra al motor principal de la nave. Hay otros motores auxiliares, pero el nuestro es el más potente. Vamos, que nuestro trabajo es muy importante».

languages.text: 「私たちは、この部屋を誇りに思っています。ここから船の主エンジンに電力を供給しています。船には他にも駆動装置がありますが、我々のものが最も強力です。つまり、我々は重要な仕事をしているのです」
languages.original_text: "We are proud of our chambers. Power feeds the ship's main engine from here. There are other drives on the ship, but ours is the mightiest. That's to say, we do important work."

languages.text: “大家都为这片甲板感到自豪。供给主引擎的电力就是从这片甲板出去的，虽说船上还有其他引擎，但我们的引擎是最有劲儿的。换句话说，我们在做着重要的工作。”
languages.original_text: "We are proud of our chambers. Power feeds the ship's main engine from here. There are other drives on the ship, but ours is the mightiest. That's to say, we do important work."

languages.text: "Wir sind stolz auf unsere Kammern. Von hier wird das Haupttriebwerk des Schiffs mit Energie versorgt. Es gibt noch andere Antriebe auf dem Schiff, aber unserer ist der stärkste. Wir verrichten also eine wichtige Arbeit.
languages.original_text: "We are proud of our chambers. Power feeds the ship's main engine from here. There are other drives on the ship, but ours is the mightiest. That's to say, we do important work."

languages.text: « Nos salles, qui alimentent le moteur principal du vaisseau, font notre fierté. Il y a d'autres réacteurs, certes, mais le nôtre est sans conteste le plus puissant. En d'autres termes, notre travail est capital. »

languages.text: "Odalarımızla gurur duyuyoruz. Makinenin ana motorunu besleyen güç buradan geliyor. Gemide başka iticiler de mevcut ancak en kudretlisi bizimki. Yani demem o ki burada önemli bir iş yapıyoruz."
languages.original_text: "We are proud of our chambers. Power feeds the ship's main engine from here. There are other drives on the ship, but ours is the mightiest. That's to say, we do important work."
